      data:
        difficulty: 0
        question:
        - Determine whether the statement is True or False. The gravitational force
          becomes weaker when the distance between two objects increases.
        - Determine whether the statement is True or False. Gravity weakens when
          the distance between two objects grows.
        - Determine whether the statement is True or False. The farther apart two
          objects are, the weaker the gravity between them.
